{"singlePage": [], "startSite": "", "filingNum": "", "onePageListNum": 15, "commentLabelColor": "#006b75", "yearColorList": ["#bc4c00", "#0969da", "#1f883d", "#A333D0"], "i18n": "CN", "themeMode": "manual", "dayTheme": "light", "nightTheme": "dark", "urlMode": "pinyin", "script": "", "style": "", "head": "", "indexScript": "", "indexStyle": "", "bottomText": "", "showPostSource": 1, "iconList": {}, "UTC": 8, "rssSplit": "sentence", "exlink": {}, "needComment": 1, "allHead": "", "title": "\u8070\u660e\u7684\u6295\u8cc7\u7d44\u5408", "subTitle": "QQQ\u4e00\u7d44\u8070\u660e\u7684\u7d44\u5408\u3002", "avatarUrl": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "GMEEK_VERSION": "last", "postListJson": {"P3": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/QQQ-tou-zi-ce-lve.html", "labels": ["Investment"], "postTitle": "QQQ\u6295\u8d44\u7b56\u7565", "postUrl": "post/QQQ-tou-zi-ce-lve.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/kcfevolve/kcfevolve.github.io/issues/3", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 1470, "description": "**\u4e0d\u8981\u8cb7\u4fdd\u96aa\u3001\u4e0d\u8981\u8cb7\u5e74\u91d1\u3001\u4e0d\u8981\u8cb7\u50b5\u5238![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5ff30fcb-71a0-4231-877f-e5638acd41ad)**\n\n\u6295\u8cc7\u7b2c\u4e00\u5802\u8ab2\uff1a\u50f9\u503c\u4e00\u5104\u5143\u6295\u8cc7\u4eba\u751f\n\n\u4fdd\u96aa\u7684\u771f\u76f8\u2014\u8cb7\u4fdd\u96aa\u6c38\u9060\u8667\u640d\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1764577129, "style": "", "script": "", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "createdDate": "2025-12-01", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P4": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/tou-zi-S&P500-zai-rui-dian-you-shen-me-xuan-ze.html", "labels": ["Investment"], "postTitle": "\u6295\u8d44S&P500\u5728\u745e\u5178\u6709\u4ec0\u4e48\u9009\u62e9", "postUrl": "post/tou-zi-S%26P500-zai-rui-dian-you-shen-me-xuan-ze.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/kcfevolve/kcfevolve.github.io/issues/4", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 5402, "description": "<div class='text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)'><div data-conversation-screenshot-content='' class='[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn'><div class='flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow'><div data-message-author-role='assistant' data-message-id='dc20b2a2-9dd5-4cde-b88c-679eeea8bf02' dir='auto' data-message-model-slug='gpt-5-5' class='min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1'><div class='flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden'><div class='markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling'><p data-start='0' data-end='70' class='PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer'>\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u4f4f\u5728\u745e\u5178\uff08\u7a0e\u52a1\u5c45\u6c11\uff09\uff0c\u60f3\u6295\u8d44\u7f8e\u56fd\u6807\u666e500\u6307\u6570\uff08S&amp;P 500\uff09\uff0c<strong data-start='36' data-end='61'>\u4e00\u822c\u4e0d\u5efa\u8bae\u76f4\u63a5\u4e70\u7f8e\u56fd\u4e0a\u5e02\u7684 SPY ETF</strong>\uff0c\u539f\u56e0\u4e3b\u8981\u6709\u4e24\u70b9\uff1a<span aria-hidden='true' class='PDq2pG_selectionAnchor'></span></p>\n<ol data-start='72' data-end='193'>\n<li data-section-id='10kfymh' data-start='72' data-end='142'>\n<strong data-start='75' data-end='91'>\u6b27\u6d32\u6cd5\u89c4\uff08PRIIPs\uff09</strong>\uff1a\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u6b27\u6d32\u96f6\u552e\u6295\u8d44\u8005\u4e0d\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u8d2d\u4e70\u7f8e\u56fd\u6ce8\u518cETF\uff0c\u4f8b\u5982 SPDR S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1782809973, "style": "", "script": "", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-06-30", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P5": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/Sweden and are a Swedish tax resident, buy the U.S.-listed SPY ETF.html", "labels": ["Investment"], "postTitle": "Sweden and are a Swedish tax resident, buy the U.S.-listed SPY ETF", "postUrl": "post/Sweden%20and%20are%20a%20Swedish%20tax%20resident%2C%20buy%20the%20U.S.-listed%20SPY%20ETF.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/kcfevolve/kcfevolve.github.io/issues/5", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 4129, "description": "<p data-start='0' data-end='157' class='PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer'>If you live in Sweden and are a Swedish tax resident, it's generally <strong data-start='69' data-end='119'>not recommended to buy the U.S.-listed SPY ETF</strong> directly. There are two main reasons:<span aria-hidden='true' class='PDq2pG_selectionAnchor'></span></p>\n<ol data-start='159' data-end='515'>\n<li data-section-id='zsh2ix' data-start='159' data-end='352'>\n<strong data-start='162' data-end='184'>PRIIPs regulations</strong>: Most retail investors in Europe cannot buy U.S.-domiciled ETFs such as SPDR S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust because they do not provide the required Key Information Document (KID).\n</li>\n<li data-section-id='61hjb2' data-start='353' data-end='515'>\n<strong data-start='356' data-end='375'>U.S. estate tax</strong>: Holding U.S.-domiciled ETFs may expose non-U.S. investors to U.S. estate tax if the value of their U.S. assets exceeds certain thresholds.\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-start='517' data-end='689'>Instead, most investors in Sweden choose <strong data-start='558' data-end='572'>UCITS ETFs</strong>, which are European-domiciled funds that track the same S&amp;P 500 Index while being more tax- and regulation-friendly.</p>\n<p data-start='691' data-end='733'>Here are some of the most popular options:</p>\n<div class='TyagGW_tableContainer'><div tabindex='-1' class='group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit'>\nETF | Ticker | TER | Notes\n-- | -- | -- | --\niShares Core S&P 500 UCITS ETF | SXR8 (EUR) / CSPX (USD) | 0.07% | One of the most popular; accumulating (reinvests dividends).\nVanguard S&P 500 UCITS ETF | VUAA | 0.07% | Vanguard's accumulating version.\nSPDR S&P 500 UCITS ETF | SPYL | 0.03% | Very low expense ratio.\nInvesco S&P 500 UCITS ETF | SPXS | ~0.05% | Another low-cost alternative.\n\n</div></div>\n<p data-start='1158' data-end='1334'>If you're investing through a Swedish broker such as <span class='hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline'><span class='whitespace-normal'>Avanza</span></span> or <span class='hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline'><span class='whitespace-normal'>Nordnet</span></span>, you should have access to these UCITS ETFs.</p>\n<h3 data-section-id='vy2chn' data-start='1336' data-end='1357'>My recommendation</h3>\n<p data-start='1359' data-end='1466'>If you're investing for the long term (10+ years) and don't need dividend income, I'd suggest one of these:</p>\n<ul data-start='1468' data-end='1614'>\n<li data-section-id='4na7st' data-start='1468' data-end='1503'>\n<strong data-start='1470' data-end='1478'>VUAA</strong> \u2013 Vanguard, accumulating\n</li>\n<li data-section-id='17agz4z' data-start='1504' data-end='1545'>\n<strong data-start='1506' data-end='1521'>SXR8 / CSPX</strong> \u2013 iShares, accumulating\n</li>\n<li data-section-id='uwagtq' data-start='1546' data-end='1614'>\n<strong data-start='1548' data-end='1556'>SPYL</strong> \u2013 Lowest expense ratio among the major S&amp;P 500 UCITS ETFs\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start='1616' data-end='1708'>Accumulating ETFs automatically reinvest dividends, which can improve long-term compounding.</p>\n<h3 data-section-id='1pkm4f7' data-start='1710' data-end='1744'>If you're using an ISK account</h3>\n<p data-start='1746' data-end='1837'>Many investors in Sweden hold these ETFs inside an <strong data-start='1797' data-end='1828'>ISK (Investeringssparkonto)</strong> because:</p>\n<ul data-start='1838' data-end='1988'>\n<li data-section-id='n80jss' data-start='1838' data-end='1900'>\nYou don't need to calculate capital gains tax on every sale.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id='1nc92x4' data-start='1901' data-end='1931'>\nThe tax reporting is simple.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id='1cde1t8' data-start='1932' data-end='1988'>\nIt's generally very efficient for long-term investing.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start='1990' data-end='2139' data-is-last-node='' data-is-only-node=''>An <strong data-start='1993' data-end='2051'>ISK account combined with a low-cost UCITS S&amp;P 500 ETF</strong> (such as VUAA or SXR8) is a common long-term investment strategy for Swedish residents.</p>\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1782810966, "style": "", "script": "", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "createdDate": "2026-06-30", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}}, "singeListJson": {}, "labelColorDict": {"bug": "#d73a4a", "Credit Card": "#800794", "documentation": "#0075ca", "duplicate": "#cfd3d7", "enhancement": "#a2eeef", "good first issue": "#7057ff", "help wanted": "#008672", "invalid": "#e4e669", "Investment": "#993db7", "question": "#d876e3", "wontfix": "#ffffff"}, "displayTitle": "\u8070\u660e\u7684\u6295\u8cc7\u7d44\u5408", "faviconUrl": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/224014623?u=d33d57c0c595eb0c7cbe3df1a9769703e0546d54&v=4", "primerCSS": "<link href='https://mirrors.sustech.edu.cn/cdnjs/ajax/libs/Primer/21.0.7/primer.css' rel='stylesheet' />", "homeUrl": "https://kcfevolve.github.io", 